										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The competitive crypto arena is officially open as Binance Wallet unrolls its latest high-stakes token event on its early-stage launchpad. The </span><b>Binance Alpha Nesa Trading Competition</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has arrived, giving eligible Web3 traders a premier opportunity to trade Nesa (NES) tokens and secure exclusive rewards.</span></p>
