					<description><![CDATA[<p>TwelveLabs Raises $100 Million to Expand Video AI Platform TwelveLabs has raised $100 million to accelerate development of artificial intelligence platforms. The investment was co-led by NEA and NAVER Ventures.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/twelvelabs-raises-100m-series-b-to-advance-video-intelligence/" data-wpel-link="internal">TwelveLabs Raises $100M Series B to Advance Video Intelligence</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
