<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pick your payment method — bank transfer, card, or one of the third-party providers.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re sending crypto in, copy your Binance wallet address (or use the QR) and send it from your other wallet.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Remember: you need to put in at least $50 within 14 days to actually get the <strong>VB2025</strong> reward.</span></li>
