<p>The Binance referral program rewards both sides when someone signs up with a shared code. New users get a signup bonus or fee discount, the referrer gets a one-time reward or ongoing commission.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">At the end of the day, it’s a growth tool. Binance ties rewards directly to user activity, so current members have a reason to tell their friends, and newcomers get a small financial boost for starting out. </span></p>
