		<title>What is Slippage in Crypto &#038; How to Avoid It? (Guide)</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/what-is-slippage-in-crypto/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Staff Reporter]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 22:00:10 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Cryptocurrency]]></category>
